I know nothing about the Middle Mountains - I have no business there. Better ask your friend the Craftsman, he always goes there for stones. Mind you, Babur means nothing to me... as far as I am concerned the Lizards can devour him alive... but they do not bother him at all - 'tis as if he were charmed!
