No. Why?
#ANIMATION 1
#CAMERA 5
#phrase Hero  5
I think it is time to play a little joke on the Craftsman - just to show him he should not be so greedy.
#ANIMATION 9
#CAMERA 9
#phrase Sheriff  6
In that case I do know where he gets his stones. You see, Babur is a suspicious character, so I told someone to follow him. Babur went right into the Middle Mountains, took the road east and did not leave it until he reached the Remote Mountains. There is a rather weird place there: four pillars with a fire burning on top of each.
#ANIMATION 44
#CAMERA 3
#phrase Sheriff  7
I do not know who put those pillars there, but they make a good landmark. The Lizards' altar with a large Shell on top lies to the north of the pillars.  And Babur's quarry is further to the north. So there!
